{"tid":2357442,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Model Y訂單超乎預期 交車將延至Q2 蔚來傳遇退單潮","createTime":"2021-01-07T12:09:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T15:03:30.000Z","uid":295230,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7a9e6dcff36d0fcc3d879b5372ca2e4c298277a5","tid":2357442,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:09:11.000Z","msg":"特斯拉在 2021 年來臨之際宣布，中國上海製 Model Y 大降價，售價已比中國當地車企蔚來汽車等還便宜，引發市場熱潮。<br />\n<br />\n特斯拉在中國的 Model Y 售價已降至 33.9 萬元人民幣，較此前預售價 48.8 萬元大幅下降，如今已比蔚來汽車的 EC6 跨界車還便宜近一成，引起了中國民眾的追捧。有輿論指出，這簡直就像是拋售大白菜，在假日期間特斯拉門市直接被塞爆，連試駕可能都要排到 2~3 個月以後了。<br />\n<br />\n據傳，在降價消息公之後僅 10 個小時內，Model Y 就收穫近 10 萬輛訂單相當可觀，雖然這可能有誇大的成份。但依這個破盤價，成績不可能會差，特斯拉官網也一度被癱瘓。這近 14 多萬人民幣的降價幅度，驚動了整個市場，輿論擔憂中國自身的廠商可能將遭遇重擊，中國媒體已有報導指出，蔚來汽車出現退訂潮，原本計畫買 ES6 的車主正轉投特斯拉，而小鵬汽車恐怕也不樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》報導，網站稱現在下定的基本版Model Y將在Q2交車、性能版更要延到Q3；特斯拉代表週四亦通過微信表示，基於訂單量和生產計劃，最新訂單的Model Y交付時間調整為第2季。中製Model Y起價為33萬9900元人民幣（約新台幣147萬2800元），性能版起價為36萬9900元人民幣（約新台幣160萬2790元）。"},{"pid":"200e88ba6dc4ca14da2fd0c5e566f832a7eaf382","tid":2357442,"uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:10:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3403945\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3403945&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6zxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=8f65385e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3403945&h=37f52ac9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3403945</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2021/01/04/teslas-price-cut-in-china-weilai-automobile-is-rumored-to-encounter-a-wave-of-back-orders/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2021%2F01%2F04%2Fteslas-price-cut-in-china-weilai-automobile-is-rumored-to-encounter-a-wave-of-back-orders%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6zxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=50bfebc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2021/01/04/teslas-price-cut-in-china-weilai-automobile-is-rumored-to-encounter-a-wave-of-back-orders/</a>"},{"pid":"8bb14d157ea0a1571cd063e13adc5e2bdfaee5da","tid":2357442,"uid":26183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:39:32.000Z","msg":"希望香港都跟住一樣減<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dcf01891790addb1d24528f70f1d98534603273","tid":2357442,"uid":4258,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:44:09.000Z","msg":"中國人連電暖爐都無電開，點會有電開tesla, 一定係fake news"},{"pid":"d0455800d6b4f0948e17e1c668a2e03facc74170","tid":2357442,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bb14d157ea0a1571cd063e13adc5e2bdfaee5da","tid":2357442,"uid":26183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:39:32.000Z","msg":"希望香港都跟住一樣減<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:45:20.000Z","msg":"中国內循環無香港人份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af412ed10d7ac7a3b647ac8881ffe7f31c46ad1","tid":2357442,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bb14d157ea0a1571cd063e13adc5e2bdfaee5da","tid":2357442,"uid":26183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:39:32.000Z","msg":"希望香港都跟住一樣減<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536dc1411bd71e30950f5303b244e7ce7b96cdea","tid":2357442,"uid":227275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8bb14d157ea0a1571cd063e13adc5e2bdfaee5da","tid":2357442,"uid":26183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:39:32.000Z","msg":"希望香港都跟住一樣減<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:12:27.000Z","msg":"香港點會減<br />\n無可能 大把人貴一貴都買得起<br />\n條路塞到仆街"},{"pi